description: This Chainlink VRF top 10% score Gaston purrs with a rating of 52, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 156, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, 2 for East, 1 for South, and Leverage for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60523-92160-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [156 Votes, Top 10% Score]
